Se0vaCG0anw</a><br />\n最近有唔少日本傳統企業開始推出vtuber,<br />\n而且好多nico大手都開始轉生做vtuber<br />\n<br />\nSUNTORY三得利  燦鳥ノム<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sPpxwKh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsPpxwKh.jpg&h=e1cd9f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwRKt_raV3N5KZgxcFyC1vw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCwRKt_raV3N5KZgxcFyC1vw&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=e0952c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwRKt_raV3N5KZgxcFyC1vw</a><br />\n樂敦製藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnDZwUFMzqOBcF3bjRfZD-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCnDZwUFMzqOBcF3bjRfZD-g&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=388e9cfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnDZwUFMzqOBcF3bjRfZD-g</a><br />\n<br />\nウェザーニュース ウェザーロイド Airi（ポン子）<br />\nweathernews既天氣主播, 2012年開始以3D登場,主要職責係天氣預報節目播報天氣,<br />\n係vtuber一詞未出現前就進行類似既直播.曾因節目方針改面一度面臨廢棄危機,但適逢vtuber潮流開始興起,同埋過往一d直播精華備受關注,知名度上升,因此得以以vtuber名義繼續活動,報導天氣資訊.2018年5月開設youtube帳號<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">經理人為社內資歷最深主播山岸愛梨.</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/weatheroidAiriChannel/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2FweatheroidAiriChannel%2Fvideos&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=b435d81e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/weatheroidAiriChannel/videos</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjiCDtF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjiCDtF.jpg&h=16baa754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有部分知名作品既角色都以vtuber出現 <br />\n有時係由原作既聲優配音,多數目標係宣傳個作品,<br />\n例如妹妹公主,小雙俠,馬娘, ハート様<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oYz6N9q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoYz6N9q.jpg&h=6d518ac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pc61B2L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpc61B2L.jpg&h=faa25e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uh9uLWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUh9uLWr.jpg&h=d8d3b743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左以短片為主亦都有以生放用(live)為主既vtuber<br />\n<br />\n講起開live就唔可以唔講<span class=\"red\">にじさんじ</span> (彩虹社)<br />\n<img src=\"https://secure-dcdn.cdn.nimg.jp/nicochannel/material/design/4067553/1223KVTOP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure-dcdn.cdn.nimg.jp%2Fnicochannel%2Fmaterial%2Fdesign%2F4067553%2F1223KVTOP.png&h=0f2ba982&s={SIZE}\" /><p class=\"left\"><p class=\"left\"></p></p>"},{"pid":"8b7cd1ba0b31190039d2f6d8f84c4a8d1c8c6ad7","tid":2291045,"uid":55384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"にじさんじ一開始只係一間想推廣自己個2D live app既公司 ,一開始招募左8個一期生 <br />\n由月ノ美兎為首其下liver人氣好高,令到にじさんじ轉型左做一間vtuber既事務所 <br />\n值得一提既係にじさんじ一開始係一間好垃圾既公司,只係提供一部iphone比成員開live <br />\n好多成員一開始開live都成問題, 不過轉型左之後睇得出進步左好多,開始提供唔少活動,仲開始搞3d ,幫成員加唔少新衫同配件,對員工有唔少輔助,近期搞唔少live等既線下活動<br />\n而家成員已經超過100人,社內風氣非常自由 <br />\n早期最出名既成員 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XY4NkDW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXY4NkDW.jpg&h=a978342b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n月ノ美兎 (委員長) <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCD-miitqNY3nyukJ4Fnf4_A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCD-miitqNY3nyukJ4Fnf4_A&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=5ed03854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCD-miitqNY3nyukJ4Fnf4_A</a><br />\n静凛 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6oDys1BGgBsIC3WhG1BovQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC6oDys1BGgBsIC3WhG1BovQ&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=347563ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6oDys1BGgBsIC3WhG1BovQ</a><br />\n樋口楓 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsg-YqdqQ-KFF0LNk23BY4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCsg-YqdqQ-KFF0LNk23BY4A&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=a361b9f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsg-YqdqQ-KFF0LNk23BY4A</a><br />\n成員表<br />\n<a href=\"https://nijisanji.ichikara.co.jp/member/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnijisanji.ichikara.co.jp%2Fmember%2F&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=91248a54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nijisanji.ichikara.co.jp/member/</a><br />\n積極招募好多新血,有超過50人超過10萬sub <br />\n <br />\n繼彩虹社之後其他公司都開始玩2D live同開始組團 <br />\n其中比較出名既有 <br />\n開始3D化既ホロライブ (ときのそら既公司) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKRabmj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKRabmj.jpg&h=66277729&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n出道時當時比起營運Fans比較痴線 部分 ときのそら既fans唔鐘意2d live成員既路線 <br />\n好彩既係第一期白上靠努力成功跑出,3期生同4期生之後發展得唔錯 <br />\n近期海外fans數目大增,5期更加一出道光速突破十萬sub <br />\n為英文市場推出既hololive EN人氣好高<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cOi9FVe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcOi9FVe.jpg&h=d3c49870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中Gawr Gura更加係1個半月內成為第一位直播勢金盾 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Qp47D5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Qp47D5.jpg&h=d6525fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前已經有3位成員一百萬sub<br />\n<br />\n成員表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hololive.tv/member\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hololive.tv%2Fmember&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=85829dbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hololive.tv/member</a><br />\n <br />\n.LIVE アイドル部(電脳少女シロ既公司)  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t1qwNnY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft1qwNnY.jpg&h=4adfb30f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<del>比較有良心既公司,同其他公司唔同每日一定會出行程表,唔會有突擊生放送,時間會控制係一小時之內,教埋成員點直播,冇電腦仲會送埋 <br />\n比較易追,所以都有唔少箱推,目前已經全部3D化,自成一箱</del> <br />\n2019年10月開始一連串既營運操作失誤同成員之間既鞭屍行為令アイドル部依個brand完全崩壞 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AwBp0g8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwBp0g8.png&h=17b18d9c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n再加上比人爆左原來冇咩錢入到成員袋 <br />\n由全盛直播時間長駐8000人去到得返3000人多D,sub數不停跌 <br />\n詳情可以睇下 <br />\n.LIVE偶像部崩壞始末(殘體慎入) <br />\n<a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/thread-1889831-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbs.saraba1st.com%2F2b%2Fthread-1889831-1-1.html&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=69437272\" target=\"_blank\">https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/thread-1889831-1-1.html</a> <br />\n <br />\n同合作用彩虹社個app做2D liver 有閑喫茶あにまーれ  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Q1LRMC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Q1LRMC.jpg&h=29493230&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2020加入左新成員去補返退出既2人 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azrx4Z5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fazrx4Z5.png&h=7e83d055&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n同 ハニーストラップ <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHup7j7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHup7j7.jpg&h=28c34fbd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n後續加左個分團叫ブイアパ <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HaUSZsq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHaUSZsq.jpg&h=b65db062&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n再個分團叫シュガーリリック<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NRzGSNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNRzGSNE.jpg&h=a24ad83d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n統稱做774箱, <br />\n成員表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.774.ai/member\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.774.ai%2Fmember&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5volgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=9d291143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht